Keep these considerations in mind when switching to the Query Editor to update a query.

Column Names, Hidden Columns, Column Formatting, and Conditional Formatting:
Column enhancements that are done in the CRM Analytics interface aren't preserved when you switch to the Query Editor and must be reapplied. 

Projected Field Names and Subtotals
If you change a projected field name within the Query Editor, ensure that its corresponding projected subtotal field name is updated to match.
